dct_description_sm: Each map includes a small cartouche surrounded by figures representing the continents.

Asiae - "II. Th. pag. 21." at top right and "G. Haupt Sc." at lower right. Europae - "II. Th. pag. 20." at top right and "G Haupt Sc." at lower right. Africae - "II. Th. pag. 26." at top right and "G Haupt Sc. a. v." at lower left.
